           SHORT="Sysvinit patched to use alternate inittab for openrc"

cat << EOF
Init is the parent of all processes. Its primary role is to create processes
from a script stored in the file /etc/openrc/inittab.
This package also contains well-known and used utilities like reboot, shutdown,
killall, poweroff, tellinit, sulogin, wall, etc.
